    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "Once you imbibe this bitter elixir, your skin exudes a toxin for 1 hour, affecting any creature that hits you with a jaws Strike or other bite attack. If you are Swallowed Whole by another creature, they are automatically exposed to the poison every round and take a \u20132 penalty to their saving throw against it.  \n  \n **Frogskin Tincture Poison** (poison)",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 6,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
